org.hkijena.jipipe.api.algorithm

Class JIPipeAlgorithm

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hkijena.jipipe.api.algorithm.JIPipeGraphNode
      • org.hkijena.jipipe.api.algorithm.JIPipeAlgorithm
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JIPipeValidatable, JIPipeParameterCollection
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CollectDataAlgorithm, DefineRectangularRoiAlgorithm, FileDataSource, FileListDataSource, FolderDataSource, FolderListDataSource, GraphWrapperAlgorithm, ImageTypeConverter, IOInterfaceAlgorithm, JIPipeParameterSlotAlgorithm, MergeDataSlots, ModifyAndMergeTablesScript, MultiParameterAlgorithm, ParametersDataDefinition, ParametersDataTableDefinition, PlotGeneratorAlgorithm, PythonScriptAlgorithm, SplitByAnnotation, TablesFromScript

    public abstract class JIPipeAlgorithm
extends JIPipeGraphNode
    An JIPipeGraphNode that contains a non-empty workload. This class contains additional parameters to control the workload behavior. Please prefer to use this class or its derivatives if you write your algorithms.
